<h1>You've been invited to join <%= @account.name %></h1>

<p><%= @inviter_email %> has invited you to join their team on mbuzz.</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Accept Invitation", accept_invitation_url(token: @token) %>
</p>

<p>This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>

<p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
